<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>التَّصْحِيفُ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>٧٧٢. وَالْعَسْكَرِيْ وَالدَّارَقُطْنِيْ صَنَّفَا … فِيمَا لَهُ بَعْضُ الرُّوَاةِ صَحَّفَا<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>٧٧٣. فِي الْمَتْنِ؛ كَالصُّولِيِّ <span style="color:#6c6c00">«سِتّاً»</span> غَيَّرْ … <span style="color:#6c6c00">«شَيْئاً»</span>، أَوِ الْإِسْنَادِ كَـ <span style="color:#6c6c00">«ابْنِ النُّدَّرْ»</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>٧٧٤.<span style="color:#006d98"> صَحَّفَ فِيهِ الطَّبَرِيُّ قَالَا:</span> … <span style="color:#6c6c00">«بُذَّرُ»</span> بِالْبَاءِ وَنَقْطٍ ذَالَا<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>٧٧٥. وَأَطْلَقُوا <span style="color:#6c6c00">«التَّصْحِيفَ»</span> فِيمَا ظَهَرَا … كَقَوْلِهِ: <span style="color:#6c6c00">«احْتَجَمْ»</span> مَكَانَ <span style="color:#6c6c00">«احْتَجَرَا»</span><a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>٧٧٦. وَوَاصِلٌ بِعَاصِمٍ وَالْأَحْدَبُ … بِأَحْوَلٍ <span style="color:#6c6c00">«تَصْحِيفَ سَمْعٍ»</span> لَقَّبُوا<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>٧٧٧. وَصَحَّفَ الْمَعْنَى إِمَامُ عَنَزَهْ … ظَنَّ الْقَبِيلَ بِحَدِيثِ <span style="color:#6c6c00">«الْعَنَزَهْ»</span><a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>٧٧٨.<span style="color:#006d98"> وَبَعْضُهُمْ ظَنَّ سُكُونَ نُونِهِ … فَقَالَ:</span> <span style="color:#6c6c00">«شَاةٍ»</span>! خَابَ فِي ظُنُونِهِ<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>